PRODUCT_DESCRIPTION: The Crosby 22.25" 5 light Chandelier features a contemporary style with its clean lines and metal accents in Chrome finish and clear glass. The Crosby chandelier works in several aesthetic environments, including traditional and modern.
This Mid-Century 10 light chandelier in Black from the Armstrong collection features a "sputnik" design with adjustable arms allowing you to customize the light for just the right look.

Titus 8 Light Oval Chandelier/Pendant features black mesh ironwork, giving off an industrial accent to a modernly sleek collection. The Chandelier/Pendant has a Polished Nickel finish for a dynamic effect.
